STATE
v.
Steve MORRISON. No. 289P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Peter S. Gilchrist, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st day of June 2006 by Defendant for Discretionary Review:
